{
  "stem": "14251.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the woman behind the counter, the owner of that greengrocery, was giving him some things that she actually was forbidden by law to give him, and he was very, very nervous and upset because now this young woman had witnessed this.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This could get the greengrocery in trouble, as well as him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when the young woman left, it turned out that was her niece, was a university student.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think it was the Humboldt University in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he had that card, but I don't think he had made the connection yet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The emergency had all happened differently.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He never got to use the ax he kept by his front door where we last lived before the attic.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because he had always said, if they come in here for us, one of them is going with me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'll whack him in the head with the ax.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember the ax standing there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was just standing there without a cover or anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And somehow, it made him secure, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Nothing came as he thought it would.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it hadn't occurred to him yet that he could call on these, that these might be OK people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This was not a trap or a come-on or anything of the kind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So that was the beginning of our being on our own.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Well, we had to get some semblance of order to what we were doing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I remember we stopped at my grandfather's apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Grandfather, my mother's sister, and the husband lived in the same apartment and had since the marriage of the sister the year before.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That way they were able to stay living there and didn't have to have other strange people in there because it wasn't a big place.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
